  <brief_title>A Randomized Study of Whether Alfuzosin(Xatral) Helps in the Passage of Kidney Stones</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blinded Placebo-Controlled Trial of Alfuzosin (Xatral)in the Management of Distal Ureteral Calculi</official_title>
